Name: Hentai Sudoku
About the game: Hentai Sudoku is a sudoku game. Gameplay Guide Victory Condition: You need to finish the sudoku. How to Play: Left click on left-menu to pick the number, and left click finish main panel. Function Keys Keyboard P: One key finish Keyboard S: Emergency avoidance (the background image turns white and you can continue to play) Keyboard N: Next level Game Features Pleasing Pictures Soothing Music
